data.description: INVESTOR ALERT! Great little home for the first time homebuyer or would make a great rental.... Home being sold as/is, hence the price. Open living/dining room with newer laminate flooring and newer windows.. 2 bedrooms on the main floor. Kitchen has nice oak cabinetry and a pantry. 3rd bedroom is on lower level and has a new egress window.   All kitchen appliances stay including washer and dryer.  There is a single car, detached garage in back with alley access but Garage adds no value to property.
